title: EstroMetab 5
description: EstroMetab 2.0 is composed of dietary supplements that help with estrogen metabolism in women and in men, helping them to maintain healthy body composition. EstroMetab 2.0 contains the herb kudzu and the nutrient DIM (diindolylmethane), which both help to improve estrogen (estrone, estriol, estradiol) levels and metabolism in the body. Grape seed extract is an important antioxidant and has aromatase inhibiting properties, which helps process estrogens in men and women.
